<http://www.spektrix.com/factorytheatre/event/142002ABJJLLLQNTLVSVVGSMTDDLHPPRK> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "UTCMC 13th CMC K-King Competition Grand Final 第十三届 CMC K王争霸赛决赛";
  schema:description """
	UTCMC's 13th K-King Competition (K王争霸赛) is back and bigger than ever! Proudly presented by the University of Toronto Chinese Music Club in collaboration with the Factory Theatre, this year's stage will feature 15 of the top singers go head-to-head in an electrifying night of music and talent. Cheer on your favourite performers, compete for incredible awards, and get ready for exciting lucky draws and plenty of surprises you won't want to miss. Grab your tickets now and be part of the magic!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>UTCMC第13届K王争霸赛强势回归! 本次活动由多伦多大学中国音乐社（UTCMC）主办，并与 Factory Theatre 合作呈现。15位实力唱将将同台竞技，在这个充满激情与音乐魅力的夜晚展开巅峰对决。为你喜爱的选手加油助威，争夺丰厚奖项，同时还有精彩的幸运抽奖和惊喜环节等你来参与。立即购票，亲临现场，让我们一起见证这场难忘的音乐盛宴！<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2> Doors at 6:30 PM | Arrive early for best possible seating!</h2>Duration: 150 mins (with intermission)<span><br/></span>Age recommendation: 12 + <span><br/></span>CW: Live and loud music<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-03-21T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/factorytheatre/files/d5a78ddf-abb7-4505-8084-a0fa6d89b5d5.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/factorytheatre/location/1AHGJDSMMPLMPPGNLJBQVLBRSKVDLQRPP>;
  schema:offers _:d25bd24b203747b0805b2b5a2fe2a792251;
  schema:duration "PT150M";
  schema:endDate "2026-03-21T22:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

